Pay tribute to departed loved ones with green methods
2012-04-03 07:59:08 GMT
Photo taken on April 2, 2012 shows flowers and silk flowers at the Jinbaoshan Cemetery in Kunming, capital of southwest China's Yunnan Province. During the Qingming Festival holiday, many people pay tribute to their departed loved ones with green methods, such as presenting flowers instead of burning joss paper.
